net.texo.USDLSecurityEditor.ui
Class UIControlBlock

java.lang.Object
  net.texo.USDLSecurityEditor.ui.UIControlBlock

public class UIControlBlock
extends java.lang.Object

Necessary to build logical units of control elements by keeping the references of all contained elements.
An UIControlBlock can contain at most two ArrayList of UIControlBlock (called 'sequence') to refer to child elements derived from the type hierarchy.
